summary: A joint U.S.-Soviet expedition is sent to Jupiter to learn what happened to the Discovery, and H.A.L.

tagline: Everything you've heard is true.
summary: The life, success and troubles of Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart, as told by Antonio Salieri, the contemporaneous composer who was insanely jealous of Mozart's talent and claimed to have murdered him.

tagline: Shocking, Shameless, Sinful, Wicked. And the party hasn't even started.
summary: A soon-to-be-married man's friends throw him the ultimate bachelor party.

tagline: The Heat Is On!
summary: A freewheeling Detroit cop pursuing a murder investigation finds himself dealing with the very different culture of Beverly Hills.

tagline: Breaking up is hard
summary: The owner of a seedy small-town Texas bar discovers that one of his employees is having an affair with his wife. A chaotic chain of misunderstandings, lies and mischief ensues after he devises a plot to have them murdered.

tagline: You can't believe everything you see.
summary: A young actor's obsession with spying on a beautiful woman who lives nearby leads to a baffling series of events with drastic consequences.

tagline: An adult nightmare.
summary: A young couple is trapped in a remote town where a dangerous religious cult of children believes that everyone over age 18 must be killed.

tagline: The most powerful legend of all is back in a new adventure.
summary: Conan leads a ragtag group of adventurers on a quest for a princess.

tagline: It is a world where sandworms 1,000 feet long guard creation's greatest treasure - the spice that prolongs life. And enables the mind to fold space and slow time. Where a prophecy will be fulfilled. And a young leader with incredible powers will emerge to command an army of five million warriors in the final battle for control of a universe and its source of ultimate power. The planet called Dune.
summary: A Duke's son leads desert warriors against the galactic emperor and his father's evil nemesis when they assassinate his father and free their desert world from the emperor's rule.

tagline: She has the power . . . an evil destructive force.
summary: A couple who participated in a potent medical experiment gain telepathic ability and then have a child who is pyrokinetic.

tagline: He's a big-city kid in a small town. They said he'd never win. He knew he had to.
summary: A city teenager moves to a small town where rock music and dancing have been banned, and his rebellious spirit shakes up the populace.

tagline: This is the one you'll be dying for...
summary: After being mortally wounded and taken to the morgue, murderer Jason Voorhees spontaneously revives and embarks on a killing spree as he makes his way back to his home at Camp Crystal Lake.

tagline: They're here to save the world.
summary: Three former parapsychology professors set up shop as a unique ghost removal service.

tagline: They didn't obey the rules
summary: A young man inadvertently breaks three important rules concerning his new pet and unleashes a horde of malevolently mischievous monsters on a small town.

primaryTitle: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom
originalTitle: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom
tagline: The man in the hat is back...
summary: In 1935, Indiana Jones arrives in India, still part of the British Empire, and is asked to find a mystical stone. He then stumbles upon a secret cult committing enslavement and human sacrifices in the catacombs of an ancient palace.

tagline: Only the 'Old One' could teach him the secrets of the masters.
summary: A martial arts master agrees to teach karate to a bullied teenager.

primaryTitle: Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind
tagline: ...the future has never been so exciting! ("Warriors of the Wind")
summary: Warrior and pacifist Princess Nausicaä desperately struggles to prevent two warring nations from destroying themselves and their dying planet.

tagline: Every so often, there is a film that is destined to be talked about and remembered for years to come.
summary: A journalist is trapped in Cambodia during tyrant Pol Pot's bloody 'Year Zero' cleansing campaign, which claimed the lives of two million 'undesirable' civilians.

tagline: In his wildest dreams, Alex never suspected that tonight he would become... the Last Starfighter.
summary: Video game expert Alex Rogan finds himself transported to another planet after conquering The Last Starfighter video game only to find out it was just a test. He was recruited to join the team of best starfighters to defend their world from the attack.

tagline: From an age of innocence comes a hero for today.
summary: A middle-aged unknown comes seemingly out of nowhere to become a legendary baseball player with almost supernatural talent.

tagline: Welcome to your nightmare.
summary: The monstrous spirit of a slain child murderer seeks revenge by invading the dreams of teenagers whose parents were responsible for his untimely death.
In a totalitarian future society, a man, whose daily work is re-writing history, tries to rebel by falling in love.

primaryTitle: Once Upon a Time in America
originalTitle: Once Upon a Time in America
tagline: As boys, they made a pact to share their fortunes, their loves, their lives. As men, they shared a dream to rise from poverty to power. Forging an empire built on greed, violence and betrayal, their dream would end as a mystery that refused to die.
summary: A former Prohibition-era Jewish gangster returns to the Lower East Side of Manhattan over thirty years later, where he once again must confront the ghosts and regrets of his old life.

tagline: A place for dreams. A place for heartbreak. A place to pick up the pieces.
summary: Travis Henderson, an aimless drifter who has been missing for four years, wanders out of the desert and must reconnect with society, himself, his life, and his family.

tagline: The new police recruits. Call them slobs. Call them jerks. Call them gross. ...Just don't call them when you're in trouble.
summary: A group of good-hearted, but incompetent misfits enter the police academy, but the instructors there are not going to put up with their pranks.

tagline: A full scale military invasion by foreign troops begins. Total surprise. Almost total success . . . .
summary: It is the dawn of World War III. In mid-western America, a group of teenagers band together to defend their town, and their country, from invading Soviet forces.

tagline: Not just a job - it's an adventure!
summary: A young punk recruited by a car repossession agency finds himself in pursuit of a Chevrolet Malibu that is wanted for a $20,000 bounty - and has something otherworldly stashed in its trunk.

tagline: They've been laughed at, picked on and put down. But now it's time for the odd to get even! Their time has come!
summary: At Adams College, a group of bullied outcasts and misfits resolve to fight back for their peace and self-respect.

tagline: She's a girl from the big city. He's a reckless soldier of fortune. For a fabulous treasure, they share an adventure no one could imagine... or survive.
summary: A mousy romance novelist sets off for Colombia to ransom her kidnapped sister, and soon finds herself in the middle of a dangerous adventure hunting for treasure with a mercenary rogue.

tagline: It's the time of your life that may last a lifetime.
summary: A girl's "sweet" sixteenth birthday becomes anything but special, as she suffers from every embarrassment possible.

tagline: Two days ago, this girl showed up naked at the Statue of Liberty. For Allen Bauer, it was love at first sight. Now, everyone is chasing her... trying to prove she's a mermaid. From the first laugh you'll be hooked.
summary: A young man is reunited with a mermaid who saved him from drowning as a boy. He falls in love with her, not knowing who or what she is.

primaryTitle: Star Trek III: The Search for Spock
originalTitle: Star Trek III: The Search for Spock
tagline: Kirk must battle the Klingons to protect the Genesis Planet and save a friend's life
summary: Admiral Kirk and his bridge crew risk their careers stealing the decommissioned U.S.S. Enterprise to return to the restricted Genesis Planet to recover Spock's body.

tagline: He has traveled from a galaxy far beyond our own. He is 100,000 years ahead of us. He has powers we cannot comprehend. And he is about to face the one force in the universe he has yet to conquer. Love.
summary: An alien takes the form of a young widow's husband and makes her drive him across the country. The government tries to stop them.
A New Yorker's life is thrown into a tailspin when his younger cousin surprise-visits him, starting a strange, unpredictable adventure.

tagline: Your future is in its hands.
summary: A human soldier is sent from 2029 to 1984 to stop an almost indestructible cyborg killing machine, sent from the same year, which has been programmed to execute a young woman whose unborn son is the key to humanity's future salvation.

tagline: Crank it to Eleven
summary: Spinal Tap, one of England's loudest bands, is chronicled by film director Marty DiBergi on what proves to be a fateful tour.

tagline: Don't tell anyone.
summary: Parody of WWII spy movies in which an American rock and roll singer becomes involved in a Resistance plot to rescue a scientist imprisoned in East Germany.

tagline: A boy who needs a friend finds a world that needs a hero in a land beyond imagination!
summary: A troubled boy dives into a wondrous fantasy world through the pages of a mysterious book.

tagline: The original may be dead... but now his bastard great-great grandson swaggers around Renaissance London with a big head and a small beard.
summary: In the Tudor court of Elizabeth I, Lord Edmund Blackadder strives to win Her Majesty's favour while attempting to avoid a grisly fate should he offend her.
Son Gokû, a fighter with a monkey tail, goes on a quest with an assortment of odd characters in search of the Dragon Balls, a set of crystals that can give its bearer anything they desire.

tagline: Meet four outrageous women who know when it comes to a good laugh, there's nothing like experience! (season 1)
summary: Four previously married women live together in Miami, sharing their various experiences together and enjoying themselves despite hard times.

tagline: His mind is the ultimate weapon.
summary: The adventures of a secret Agent armed with almost infinite scientific resourcefulness.

tagline: What if that date you thought would never end, didn't?
summary: An ordinary word processor has the worst night of his life after he agrees to visit a girl in Soho who he met that evening at a coffee shop.

tagline: He's the only kid ever to get into trouble before he was born. [UK]
summary: Marty McFly, a 17-year-old high school student, is accidentally sent thirty years into the past in a time-traveling DeLorean invented by his close friend, the eccentric scientist Doc Brown.

tagline: Teenage life has never been darker...or funnier...
summary: After his girlfriend ditches him for a boorish ski jock, Lane decides that suicide is the only answer. However, his increasingly inept attempts bring him only more agony and embarrassment. Filled with the wildest teen nightmares.

tagline: Hidden by darkness. Guarded by witches. Discovered by a boy. Stolen by a king. Whoever owns it will rule the world. Or destroy it.
summary: A young boy and a bunch of misfit friends embark on a quest to find a dark magic item of ultimate power before a diabolical tyrant can.

tagline: It's only a state of mind.
summary: A bureaucrat in a dystopic society becomes an enemy of the state as he pursues the woman of his dreams.

tagline: Five strangers with nothing in common, except each other.
summary: Five high school students meet in Saturday detention and discover how they have a lot more in common than they thought.

tagline: One man is about to make the biggest decision that will change the course of his life... financially and mentally.
summary: A minor league baseball player has to spend $30 million in thirty days, in order to inherit $300 million. However, he's not allowed to own any assets, destroy the money, gift it, give it to charity or tell anyone about the deal.

tagline: "Cluedo" isn't just a boardgame anymore!
summary: Six guests are anonymously invited to a strange mansion for dinner, but after their host is killed, they must cooperate with the staff to identify the murderer as the bodies pile up.

tagline: Cocoon have aliens.
summary: When a group of trespassing seniors swim in a pool containing alien cocoons, they find themselves energized with youthful vigor.

tagline: Alice Walker's Pulitzer Prize Winning Story.
summary: A black Southern woman struggles to find her identity after suffering abuse from her father and others over four decades.

tagline: Let's Party
summary: A retired Special Forces colonel tries to save his daughter, who was abducted by his former subordinate.

tagline: A plague that could not be stopped!
summary: A small group of military officers and scientists dwell in an underground bunker as the world above is overrun by zombies.

tagline: Enemies because they were taught to be. Survivors because they had to be.
summary: During a long space war, the lives of two wounded enemies become dependent on their ability to forgive and to trust.

tagline: Meet the only guy who changes his identity more often than his underwear.
summary: Irwin M. "Fletch" Fletcher is a newspaper reporter being offered a large sum to off a cancerous millionaire, but is on the run, risking his job and finding clues when it's clear the man is healthy.

tagline: The mindless, murderous fury that was buried with Jason has been reborn. And suddenly, terror has become child's play!
summary: Still haunted by his past, Tommy Jarvis - who, as a child, killed Jason Voorhees - wonders if the serial killer is connected to a series of brutal murders occurring in and around the secluded halfway house where he now lives.

tagline: There are some very good reasons to be afraid...of the dark.
summary: A teenager discovers that the newcomer in his neighborhood is a vampire, so he turns to an actor in a television horror show for help dealing with the undead.

tagline: The pirates map, The villainous crooks, The underground caverns, The booby traps, the skeletons, The monster, the lost treasure, and the magic that is... THE GOONIES
summary: A group of young misfits called The Goonies discover an ancient map and set out on an adventure to find a legendary pirate's long-lost treasure.

tagline: They're back again...and romancing a brand new stone.
summary: When Joan Wilder is abducted while on a trip along the Nile, her boyfriend, Jack Colton, and pal Ralph rush to rescue her and retrieve a fabled jewel.

tagline: You may know the name, but the game has changed.
summary: A virtuous Hong Kong Police Officer must clear his good name when the drug lord he is after frames him for the murder of a dirty cop.

tagline: A Magical Mystical Adventure
summary: The thief Gaston escapes the dungeon of medieval Aquila through the latrine. Soldiers are about to kill him when Navarre saves him. Navarre, traveling with his spirited hawk, plans to kill the bishop of Aquila with help from Gaston.

tagline: There may never be another dawn. (International and US Trailer)
summary: A young man must stop the Lord of Darkness from destroying daylight and marrying the woman he loves.

tagline: A lone warrior searching for his destiny...a tribe of lost children waiting for a hero...in a world battling to survive, they face a woman determined to rule.
summary: After being exiled from the most advanced town in post apocalyptic Australia, a drifter travels with a group of abandoned children to rebel against the town's queen.

tagline: Sometimes the most unlikely people become heroes.
summary: A teenager with a massive facial skull deformity and biker gang mother attempt to live as normal a life as possible under the circumstances.

tagline: For over two thousand years, Europe has survived many great disasters. Now for the real test... The Griswold's.
summary: The Griswolds win a vacation tour across Europe where the usual havoc ensues.

primaryTitle: A Nightmare on Elm Street 2: Freddy's Revenge
originalTitle: A Nightmare on Elm Street Part 2: Freddy's Revenge
tagline: The first name in terror returns...
summary: A teenage boy is haunted in his dreams by deceased child murderer Freddy Krueger, who is out to possess him in order to continue his reign of terror in the real world.

tagline: Based on a true story.
summary: In 20th-century colonial Kenya, a Danish baroness/plantation owner has a passionate love affair with a free-spirited big-game hunter.

tagline: ... and hell followed with him.
summary: A mysterious preacher (Clint Eastwood) protects a humble prospector village from a greedy mining company trying to encroach on their land.

tagline: The story of a rebel and his bike.
summary: When eccentric man-child Pee-wee Herman gets his beloved bike stolen in broad daylight, he sets out across the U.S. on the adventure of his life.

tagline: Watch out! They've got to clean up the worst crime district in the world. But that's no problem. They're the worst police force in the universe.
summary: When a new gang moves into town it's up to the screwball police team to stop them.

tagline: She's finally met the man of her dreams. He's not real but you can't have everything. [Video]
summary: In New Jersey in 1935, a movie character walks off the screen and into the real world.

tagline: No man, no law, no war can stop him.
summary: Rambo returns to the jungles of Vietnam on a mission to infiltrate an enemy base-camp and rescue the American POWs still held captive there.

In Medieval Japan, an elderly warlord retires, handing over his empire to his three sons. However, he vastly underestimates how the new-found power will corrupt them and cause them to turn on each other...and him.

tagline: H.P. Lovecraft's classic tale of horror
summary: After an odd new medical student arrives on campus, a dedicated local and his girlfriend become involved in bizarre experiments centering around the re-animation of dead tissue.

tagline: It's yet another in a long series of diversions in an attempt to avoid responsibility.
summary: Teenage geniuses deal with their abilities while developing a high-powered laser for a university project. When their professor intends to turn their work into a military weapon, they decide to ruin his plans.

tagline: A woman and a warrior that became a legend.
summary: The fearless warrior Red Sonja sets out to avenge her family's murder and rid her kingdom from the tyrannical rule of evil Queen Gedren.

primaryTitle: The Return of the Living Dead
originalTitle: The Return of the Living Dead
tagline: They're Back From The Grave and Ready To Party!
summary: When two bumbling employees at a medical supply warehouse accidentally release a deadly gas into the air, the vapors cause the dead to rise again as zombies.

tagline: He's facing the ultimate challenge. And fighting for his life. [UK]
summary: Rocky Balboa proudly holds the world heavyweight boxing championship, but a new challenger has stepped forward: Drago, a six-foot-four, 261-pound fighter who has the backing of the Soviet Union.

tagline: The Ride Of Your Death...
summary: Two escaped convicts and a female railway worker find themselves trapped on a train with no brakes and nobody driving.

tagline: Get ready for the ride of your life.
summary: A misfit bunch of friends comes together to right the injustices which exist in a small town.

tagline: With spies like these who needs enemies?
summary: Two bumbling government employees think they are U.S. spies, only to discover that they are actually decoys for Nuclear War.

tagline: The passion burns deep.
summary: A group of friends, just out of college, struggle with adulthood.

tagline: MICHAEL J. FOX is back from the future in a NEW COMEDY...
summary: An ordinary high school student discovers that his family has an unusual pedigree when he finds himself turning into a werewolf.

primaryTitle: To Live and Die in L.A.
originalTitle: To Live and Die in L.A.
tagline: A federal agent is dead. A killer is loose. And the City of Angels is about to explode.
summary: A fearless Secret Service agent will stop at nothing to bring down the counterfeiter who killed his partner.

tagline: He was 98 lbs. of solid nerd until he became...
summary: Tromaville has a monstrous new hero. The Toxic Avenger is born when meek mop boy Melvin falls into a vat of toxic waste. Now evildoers will have a lot to lose.

tagline: Bond Is Back - Action Packed As Ever [UK poster]
summary: The recovery of a microchip off the body of a fellow agent leads James Bond to a mad industrialist who plans to create a worldwide microchip monopoly by destroying California's Silicon Valley.

tagline: If you can't get a date, make one!
summary: Two high school nerds use a computer program to literally create the perfect woman, but she turns their lives upside down.

tagline: Harrison Ford is John Book - A big city cop who knows too much. His only evidence: a small boy who's seen too much...
summary: When a young Amish boy is sole witness to a murder, policeman John Book goes into hiding in Amish country to protect him until the trial.
A furry alien wiseguy comes to live with the Tanner family after crashing into their garage.

tagline: The Wizard of Auz hits The Big Apple!
summary: An American reporter goes to the Australian outback to meet an eccentric crocodile poacher and invites him to New York City.

tagline: There are some places in the universe you don't go alone.
summary: Fifty-seven years after surviving an apocalyptic attack aboard her space vessel by merciless space creatures, Officer Ripley awakens from hyper-sleep and tries to warn anyone who will listen about the predators.

tagline: A holiday event from Universal Pictures and Amblin Entertainment.
summary: While emigrating to the United States, a young Russian mouse gets separated from his family and must relocate them while trying to survive in a new country.

tagline: Registration starts Friday, June 13, at theaters everywhere.
summary: To help his discouraged son get through college, a funloving and obnoxious rich businessman decides to enter the school as a student himself.

tagline: A Mystical, Action, Adventure, Comedy, Kung Fu, Monster, Ghost Story!
summary: A rough-and-tumble trucker helps rescue his friend's fiancée from an ancient sorcerer in a supernatural battle beneath Chinatown.

tagline: Now It's Dark.
summary: The discovery of a severed human ear found in a field leads a young man on an investigation related to a beautiful, mysterious nightclub singer and a group of psychopathic criminals who have kidnapped her child.

tagline: The strong arm of the law.
summary: A tough-on-crime street cop must protect the only surviving witness to a strange murderous cult with far-reaching plans.

tagline: The Hustler isn't what he used to be, but he has the next best thing. A kid who is.
summary: Fast Eddie Felson teaches a cocky but immensely talented protégé the ropes of pool hustling, which in turn inspires him to make an unlikely comeback.

tagline: They bite!
summary: A group of small but vicious alien creatures called Crites escape from an alien prison transport vessel and land near a small farm town on earth, pursued by two shape-shifting bounty hunters.

tagline: It's not where you start - It's where you start again.
summary: Two men are framed and sent to jail, where they meet a murderer who helps them escape and leave the state.

tagline: One Man's Struggle To Take It Easy
summary: A high school wise guy is determined to have a day off from school, despite what the Principal thinks of that.

tagline: Come along on the greatest adventure of the summer!
summary: In 1978, a boy travels 8 years into the future and has an adventure with an intelligent, wisecracking alien ship.

tagline: There is a limit, even to the imagination, where our greatest creations meet our deepest fears. Doctor Seth Brundle is about to go beyond that limit...and he's bringing you for the ride.
summary: A brilliant but eccentric scientist begins to transform into a giant man/fly hybrid after one of his experiments goes horribly wrong.

primaryTitle: Friday the 13th Part VI: Jason Lives
originalTitle: Friday the 13th Part VI: Jason Lives
tagline: Evil Lives Forever (Deluxe Edition DVD)
summary: Tommy Jarvis goes to the graveyard to get rid of Jason Voorhees' body once and for all, but inadvertently brings him back to life instead. The newly revived killer once again seeks revenge, and Tommy may be the only one who can defeat him.

tagline: Eddie Murphy Is The Chosen One.
summary: A private detective specializing in missing children is charged with the task of finding a special child whom dark forces want to eliminate.

tagline: All new! All fun!
summary: Basil, the rodent Sherlock Holmes, investigates the kidnapping of a toy maker and uncovers its link to his archenemy, Professor Ratigan.
Between two Thanksgivings two years apart, Hannah's husband falls in love with her sister Lee, while her hypochondriac ex-husband rekindles his relationship with her sister Holly.

tagline: ... the scars run deep.
summary: Hard-nosed, hard-living Marine Gunnery Sergeant Tom Highway (Clint Eastwood) clashes with his superiors and his ex-wife as he takes command of a spoiled recon platoon with a bad attitude.

tagline: He fought his first battle on the Scottish Highlands in 1536.  He will fight his greatest battle on the streets of New York City in 1986.  His name is Connor MacLeod.  He is immortal.
summary: An immortal Scottish swordsman must confront the last of his immortal opponent, a murderously brutal barbarian who lusts for the fabled "Prize".

tagline: Out on the desert highway, the rule of thumb has a different meaning...
summary: A young man who escapes the clutches of a murderous hitchhiker is subsequently stalked by the hitcher and framed for his crimes.

tagline: They needed a second chance to finish first.
summary: A coach with a checkered past and a local drunk train a small town high school basketball team to become a top contender for the championship.

tagline: You will believe that a duck can talk.
summary: A sarcastic humanoid duck is pulled from his homeworld to Earth where he must stop an alien invasion with the help of a nerdy scientist and a struggling female rock singer.
After finding an old rifle, a young boy joins the Soviet resistance movement against ruthless German forces and experiences the horrors of World War II.

tagline: The story continues...
summary: Daniel accompanies his mentor, Mr. Miyagi, to Miyagi's childhood home in Okinawa. Miyagi visits his dying father and confronts his old rival, while Daniel falls in love and inadvertently makes a new rival of his own.

tagline: Where everything seems possible and nothing is what it seems.
summary: Sixteen-year-old Sarah is given thirteen hours to solve a labyrinth and rescue her baby brother Toby when her wish for him to be taken away is granted by the Goblin King Jareth.

tagline: A Singing Plant. A Daring Hero. A Sweet Girl. A Demented Dentist.
summary: A nerdy florist finds his chance for success and romance with the help of a giant man-eating plant who demands to be fed.

tagline: (reissue) Hannibal Lecter's legacy of evil begins here.
summary: Former F.B.I. profiler Will Graham (William Petersen) returns to service to pursue a deranged serial killer named "the Tooth Fairy" (Tom Noonan) by the media.

tagline: Stephen King's masterpiece of terror directed by the master himself.
summary: A group of people try to survive when machines start to come alive and become homicidal.

tagline: Deep in the jungles of South America two men bring civilization to a native tribe. Now, after years of struggle together, they find themselves on opposite sides in a dramatic fight for the natives' independence. One will trust in the power of prayer. One will believe in the might of the sword.
summary: Eighteenth-century Spanish Jesuits try to protect a remote South American tribe in danger of falling under the rule of pro-slavery Portugal.

tagline: For everyone who's ever been deeply in Love or deeply in debt.
summary: A young couple struggles to repair a hopelessly dilapidated house.

tagline: He never bargained for what he found.
summary: An inventor spurns his city life and moves his family into the jungles of Central America to make a utopia.

tagline: Who, in the name of God, is getting away with murder?
summary: An intellectually nonconformist friar investigates a series of mysterious deaths in an isolated abbey.

tagline: Desire. Infatuation. Obsession.
summary: A woman becomes involved with a man she barely knows. Complications develop during their sexual escapades.

tagline: Knowing what you know now, what would you do differently? Peggy Sue is going back with the chance to change her destiny.
summary: Peggy Sue faints at a high school reunion. When she wakes up, she finds herself in her own past, just before she finished school.

tagline: The first casualty of war is innocence.
summary: A young soldier in Vietnam faces a moral crisis when confronted with the horrors of war and the duality of man.

tagline: The Law EnFARCEment Saga Continues!
summary: The alumni of Commandant Lassard's Police Academy (1984) return to the school to train new recruits and prevent its closure.

tagline: Blane's a pretty cool guy. Andie's pretty in pink. And Ducky's pretty crazy.
summary: A poor girl must choose between the affections of dating her childhood sweetheart or a rich but sensitive playboy.

tagline: The government gave him a raw deal. Nobody gives him a raw deal.
summary: A former FBI agent turned small-town sheriff agrees to help the FBI chief infiltrate the Chicago mafia when the FBI chief's son is killed by them.

tagline: From Merchant-Ivory, the team who brought you "THE EUROPEANS" and "HEAT AND DUST" comes a brilliant movie adaptation of E.M. Forster's classic novel "A ROOM WITH A VIEW"
summary: Lucy meets George in a Florence pensione and the two share a brief romance before Lucy returns home, where she becomes engaged to Cecil. However, it isn't long before George unexpectedly enters her life again.

tagline: Sam Stone's wife has just been kidnapped... And he doesn't want her back!
summary: A couple, cheated by a vile businessman, kidnap his wife in retaliation, without knowing that their enemy is delighted they did.

tagline: Life is not a malfunction.
summary: Number 5 of a group of experimental robots in a lab is electrocuted, suddenly becomes intelligent, and escapes.

tagline: Love kills
summary: The relationship between Sid Vicious, bassist for British punk group Sex Pistols, and his girlfriend Nancy Spungen is portrayed.

tagline: For some, it's the last real taste of innocence, and the first real taste of life. But for everyone, it's the time that memories are made of.
summary: After the death of one of his friends, a writer recounts a childhood journey with his friends to find the body of a missing boy.

primaryTitle: Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home
originalTitle: Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home
tagline: Beaming down to Earth December 12 1986
summary: To save Earth from an alien probe, Admiral James T. Kirk and his fugitive crew go back in time to San Francisco in 1986 to retrieve the only beings who can communicate with it: humpback whales.
A young boy and a girl with a magic crystal must race against pirates and foreign agents in a search for a legendary floating castle.

tagline: After a decade of silence... The buzzz is back!
summary: A radio host is victimized by the cannibal family as a former Texas Marshall hunts them.

tagline: They're Down On Their Luck And Up To Their Necks In Senoritas, Margaritas, Banditos And Bullets!
summary: Three actors accept an invitation to a Mexican village to perform their onscreen bandit fighter roles, unaware that it is the real thing.

tagline: I feel the need, the need for speed.
summary: As students at the United States Navy's elite fighter weapons school compete to be best in the class, one daring young pilot learns a few things from a civilian instructor that are not taught in the classroom.

tagline: A monster planet destroys everything in its path, while Optimus Prime and Megatron battle to the death.
summary: The Autobots must stop a colossal planet consuming robot who goes after the Autobot Matrix of Leadership. At the same time, they must defend themselves against an all-out attack from the Decepticons.

tagline: Macbeth!
summary: In the Regency era, Mr E. Blackadder serves as butler to the foppish numskull Prince George amidst the fads and crazes of the time.
The globe-trotting treasure-hunting money-making adventures of billionaire Scrooge McDuck and his nephews.
A widowed broadcaster raises his three daughters with assistance from his rock'n'roll brother-in-law and his madcap best friend.

tagline: Domestic bliss was never like this!
summary: Al Bundy is a misanthropic women's shoe salesman with a miserable life. He hates his job, his wife is lazy, his son is dysfunctional (especially with women), and his daughter is dim-witted and promiscuous.

tagline: New Stars. New Stories. New Worlds To Explore.

tagline: Sid 6.7: the ultimate killing machine
summary: When a virtual reality simulation created using the personalities of multiple serial killers manages to escape into the real world, an ex-cop is tasked with stopping its reign of terror.

tagline: A man in search. A woman in need. A story of fate.
summary: A married soldier returning from World War II poses as a pregnant woman's husband to save her from her father's anger and honor.

tagline: Beyond the horizon lies the secret to a new beginning.
summary: In a future where the polar ice-caps have melted and Earth is almost entirely submerged, a mutated mariner fights starvation and outlaw "smokers," and reluctantly helps a woman and a young girl try to find dry land.

tagline: Not all girls want to play with dolls.
summary: An awkward seventh-grader struggles to cope with inattentive parents, snobbish class-mates, a smart older brother, an attractive younger sister and her own insecurities in suburban New Jersey.

tagline: A story about love at second sight.
summary: A hopelessly romantic Chicago Transit Authority token collector is mistaken for the fiancée of a coma patient.

tagline: There's a new family in town. They're not from another city... They're from another planet.
summary: A group of aliens are sent to Earth, disguised as a human family, to experience and report life on the third planet from the sun.

tagline: The Most Important News Show... Ever
summary: A comedy news show featuring humorous takes on top stories.

tagline: He skips grades. She just skips.
summary: The misadventures of a boy genius and his annoying sister.

tagline: A comedy about a dad who just can't resist being irresistible.
summary: The comical everyday life of sports columnist Ray Barone and his dysfunctional family.

The everyday life of Arnold, a fourth-grader in a nameless city that resembles Brooklyn, New York, who lives in a multi-racial boarding house with his grandparents and a motley assortment of friends and neighbors.

tagline: She'll leave you spellbound.
summary: When a sixteen-year-old high school student finds out she's a witch, her two aunts offer guidance on how to control her newly-discovered magical powers.

tagline: Slur campaigns. Cheap shots. Smear tactics. Just another day at the office.
summary: Mike Flaherty, the Deputy Mayor of New York City, and his team of half-wits must constantly save the Mayor from embarrassment and the media. Mike is later succeeded by Charlie Crawford.

tagline: Bad to the Bone.
summary: An evil high-fashion designer plots to steal Dalmatian puppies in order to make an extravagant fur coat, but instead creates an extravagant mess.

tagline: For centuries we've been watching the skies, when we should have been watching our backs.
summary: Zane, an astronomer, discovers intelligent alien life. But the aliens are keeping a deadly secret, and will do anything to stop Zane from learning it.

tagline: Don't call me babe!
summary: During the Second American Civil War in 2017, Barb Wire owns a nightclub called the Hammerhead. Things become complicated when her ex-lover Axel Hood, who is married to the fugitive Corrina Devonshire, re-enters her life.

tagline: good times never seemed so good
summary: A piano player at a crossroads in his life returns home to his friends and their own problems with life and love.

tagline: Coming to a screen bigger than your TV.
summary: Our intrepid adolescent heroes wake up to find their beloved television stolen, and embark on an epic journey across America to recover it, and, who knows, maybe even score.

tagline: Bud and Doyle are here to save the world. But who's gonna save the world from Bud and Doyle?
summary: Moronic best friends get themselves locked inside the Bio-Dome, a science experiment, along with a group of environmental scientists for one year.

tagline: Outline description of film
summary: A gay cabaret owner and his drag queen companion agree to put up a false straight front so that their son can introduce them to his fiancée's right-wing moralistic parents.

tagline: There's one in every family.
summary: A gubernatorial candidate hires a wormy special assistant whose only job is to make sure the candidate's well-meaning but incompetent brother doesn't ruin the election.

tagline: They're not really criminals, but everybody's got to have a dream.
summary: Three friends plan to pull off a simple robbery and go on the run.

tagline: Violet and Corky are making laundry day a very big deal.
summary: Tough ex-con Corky and her lover Violet concoct a scheme to steal millions of stashed mob money and pin the blame on Violet's crooked boyfriend Caesar.

tagline: Love is a mighty power.
summary: Oilman Jan is paralyzed in an accident. His wife, who prayed for his return, feels guilty; even more, when Jan urges her to have sex with another.

tagline: Prepare to Go Ballistic
summary: Terrorists steal nuclear warheads from the U.S. military but don't count on a pilot and park ranger spoiling their plans.

tagline: Tough cop. Hostile witness.
summary: Two criminals, Keats and Moses, end their friendship, when Keats turns out to be an undercover cop. Many years later, the two are forced to work together when Keats is assigned to protect Moses as a witness.

tagline: Once you're hooked... you're his.
summary: A lonely and mentally disturbed cable guy raised on television just wants a new friend, but his target, a designer, rejects him, with bad consequences.

tagline: Reaction Time 8-4-96
summary: Two researchers in a green alternative energy project are put on the run when they are framed for murder and treason.

tagline: A medal for honor. A search for justice. A battle for truth.
summary: A U.S. Army officer, despondent about a deadly mistake he made, investigates a female chopper commander's worthiness for the Medal of Honor.

tagline: Welcome to the Witching Hour
summary: A newcomer to a Catholic prep high school falls in with a trio of outcast teenage girls who practice witchcraft, and they all soon conjure up various spells and curses against those who anger them.

tagline: Exploring the ultimate thrill where body and metal become one!
summary: After getting into a serious car accident, a TV director discovers an underground sub-culture of scarred, omnisexual car-crash victims who use car accidents and the raw sexual energy they produce to try to rejuvenate his sex life with his wife.

tagline: Arthur Miller's timeless tale of truth on trial.
summary: A Salem resident attempts to frame her ex-lover's wife for being a witch in the middle of the 1692 witchcraft trials.

tagline: no hope
summary: Disaster in a New York tunnel as explosions collapse both ends of it. One hero tries to help the people inside find their way to safety.

primaryTitle: Don't Be a Menace to South Central While Drinking Your Juice in the Hood
originalTitle: Don't Be a Menace to South Central While Drinking Your Juice in the Hood
tagline: Finally, the movie that proves that Justice isn't always Poetic, Jungle Fever isn't always pretty, and Higher Learning can be a waste of time.
summary: A parody of several U.S. films about being in the 'Hood', for instance Boyz n the Hood (1991), South Central (1992), Menace II Society (1993), Higher Learning (1995) and Juice (1992).

tagline: You will believe.
summary: The last dragon and a disillusioned dragonslaying Knight must cooperate to stop an evil King, who was given partial immortality.

tagline: Cupid is armed and dangerous!
summary: While matchmaking for friends and neighbours, a young 19th Century Englishwoman nearly misses her own chance at love.

tagline: In love, there are no boundaries.
summary: At the close of World War II, a young nurse tends to a badly-burned plane crash victim. His past is shown in flashbacks, revealing an involvement in a fateful love affair.

tagline: He will erase your past to protect your future.
summary: A Witness Protection specialist becomes suspicious of his co-workers when dealing with a case involving high-tech weapons.

tagline: Snake Is Back.
summary: Snake Plissken is once again called in by the United States government to recover a potential doomsday device from Los Angeles, now an autonomous island where undesirables are deported.
Baran the Bandit, released from prison after 35 years, searches for vengeance and his lover.
A New York girl sets her father up with a beautiful woman in a troubled marriage while her stepsister gets engaged.

tagline: The Most Anticipated Motion Picture Event of The Year
summary: The hit musical based on the life of Eva Perón (Evita Duarte), a B-picture Argentinian actress who eventually became the wife of Argentinian president Juan Domingo Perón, and the most beloved and hated woman in Argentina.

tagline: Five miles above the earth, an elite team of six men must make an air to air transfer, in order to save 400 lives on board a 747... and 40 million below.
summary: When terrorists seize control of an airliner, an intelligence analyst accompanies a commando unit for a midair boarding operation.

tagline: All baseball fans have a favorite player. This one has a favorite target.
summary: An all star baseball player becomes the unhealthy focus of a down on his luck salesman.

tagline: Small town. Big crime. Dead cold.
summary: Jerry Lundegaard's inept crime falls apart due to his and his henchmen's bungling and the persistent police work of the quite pregnant Marge Gunderson.

tagline: The attraction was obvious...The danger wasn't. Now, if he can't have her...No one will.
summary: When Nicole met David; handsome, charming, affectionate, he was everything. It seemed perfect, but soon she sees that David has a darker side. And his adoration turns to obsession, their dream into a nightmare, and her love into fear.

tagline: Don't get mad. Get everything.
summary: Reunited by the death of a college friend, three divorced women seek revenge on the husbands who left them for younger women.

tagline: No Exit
summary: A twisted take on "Little Red Riding Hood", with a teenage juvenile delinquent on the run from a social worker travelling to her grandmother's house and being hounded by a charming, but sadistic, serial killer and pedophile.

tagline: Death is no way to make a living!
summary: After a tragic car accident that kills his wife, a man discovers he can communicate with the dead to con people. However, when a demonic spirit appears, he may be the only one who can stop it from killing the living and the dead.

tagline: A terrifying evil has been unleashed. And five strangers are our only hope to stop it.
summary: Two criminals and their hostages unknowingly seek temporary refuge in a truck stop populated by vampires, with chaotic results.

tagline: Prey For The Hunters
summary: A bridge engineer and an experienced old hunter begin a hunt for two lions after they start attacking local construction workers.
Hamlet, Prince of Denmark, returns home to find his father murdered and his mother remarrying the murderer, his uncle. Meanwhile, war is brewing.

tagline: He doesn't play golf... he destroys it.
summary: A rejected hockey player puts his skills to the golf course to save his grandmother's house.
A deformed bell-ringer must assert his independence from a vicious government minister in order to help his friend, a gypsy dancer.

tagline: Don't make plans for August.
summary: The aliens are coming and their goal is to invade and destroy Earth. Fighting superior technology, mankind's best weapon is the will to survive.

tagline: The gates of hell are unlocked.
summary: After being rescued and brought to an island, a man discovers that its inhabitants are experimental animals being turned into strange-looking humans, all of it the work of a visionary doctor.

tagline: He's a healthy ten-year-old who's growing four times faster than normal. Now he's ready for the biggest adventure of his life...5th grade.
summary: Because of an unusual disorder that has aged him four times faster than a typical human being, a boy looks like a 40-year-old man as he starts fifth grade at public school after being homeschooled.

tagline: Marvellous things will happen!
summary: An orphan who lives with his two cruel aunts befriends anthropomorphic bugs who live inside a giant peach, and they embark on a journey to New York City.

tagline: The rest of his life begins now.
summary: When a sports agent has a moral epiphany and is fired for expressing it, he decides to put his new philosophy to the test as an independent agent with the only athlete who stays with him and his former colleague.

tagline: Two Dads, One Toy, No Prisoners.
summary: A father vows to get his son a Turbo Man action figure for Christmas. However, every store is sold out of them, and he must travel all over town and compete with everybody else in order to find one.

tagline: The movie the Olympuk comitee wouldn't allow you to see.
summary: A star bowler whose career was prematurely "cut off" hopes to ride a new prodigy to success and riches.

tagline: There are two sides to every war. And John Smith is on both of them.
summary: A drifting gunslinger-for-hire finds himself in the middle of an ongoing war between the Irish and Italian mafia in a Prohibition era ghost town.

tagline: John Sayles invites you to return to the scene of the crime.
summary: When the skeleton of his murdered predecessor is found, Sheriff Sam Deeds unearths many other long-buried secrets in his Texas border town.

tagline: Eight years ago she lost her memory. Now, a detective must help her remember the past before it buries them both. What's forgotten is not always gone.
summary: Samantha Caine lives in a small town with her daughter. Eight years ago she emerged, two months pregnant, from a nearby river with no memory of her past or who she is. However, she's getting closer to finding out about her past.

tagline: A lost road on the edge of strange...
summary: Anonymous videotapes presage a musician's murder conviction, and a gangster's girlfriend leads a mechanic astray.

tagline: Nice planet. We'll take it!
summary: Earth is invaded by Martians with unbeatable weapons and a cruel sense of humor.

tagline: Sometimes the people you know the least...are the ones you need the most!
summary: After seventeen years, a fiercely independent woman and her rebellious son return home and together they turn the family she left behind upside down.

tagline: A little magic goes a long way.
summary: Story of a wonderful little girl, who happens to be a genius, and her wonderful teacher vs. the worst parents ever and the worst school principal imaginable.

tagline: He's an angel... Not a saint.
summary: Two tabloid reporters checking out a report of the Archangel Michael living with an old woman find that it's true. But that's not the only surprise.

tagline: An epic tale of passion and destiny.
summary: Neil Jordan's historical biopic of Irish revolutionary Michael Collins, the man who led a guerrilla war against the UK, helped negotiate the creation of the Irish Free State, and led the National Army during the Irish Civil War.

tagline: Only the mission matters
summary: An American agent, under false suspicion of disloyalty, must discover and expose the real spy without the help of his organization.

tagline: Better living through cloning.
summary: A man who never has enough time for the things he wants to do is offered the opportunity to have himself duplicated.

tagline: Inside Sherman Klump, a party animal is about to break out.
summary: Grossly overweight yet good-hearted professor Sherman Klump takes a special chemical that turns him into the slim but obnoxious Buddy Love.

tagline: She was having a perfectly bad day... Then he came along and spoiled it.
summary: The lives of two strangers and their young children unexpectedly intersect on one hectic, stressful day in New York City.

tagline: You may not like what he does, but are you prepared to give up his right to do it?
summary: The story of controversial pornography publisher Larry Flynt, and how he became a defender of free speech.

tagline: Slam evil!
summary: The Phantom, descendent of a line of African superheroes, travels to New York City to thwart a wealthy criminal genius from obtaining three magic skulls which would give him the secret to ultimate power.

tagline: Some things in life just can't be explained.
summary: An ordinary man sees a bright light descend from the sky, and discovers he now has super-intelligence and telekinesis.

tagline: Sooner or later a man who wears two faces forgets which one is real.
summary: An altar boy is accused of murdering a priest, and the truth is buried several layers deep.

tagline: Du har ikke en chance.  Grib den.
summary: A drug pusher grows increasingly desperate after a botched deal leaves him with a large debt to a ruthless drug lord.

tagline: This Fall, pay the price
summary: Multi-millionaire Tom Mullen's son is kidnapped, but after initially agreeing to pay the ransom Mullen then decides to use the ransom money as a bounty.

tagline: America is Rocking!
summary: A mild-mannered chemist and an ex-con must lead the counterstrike when a rogue group of military men, led by a renegade general, threaten a nerve gas attack from Alcatraz against San Francisco.

tagline: Hope & Despair. Tragedy & Love. Romeo & Juliet.
summary: Shakespeare's famous play is updated to the hip modern suburb of Verona still retaining its original dialogue.

tagline: Now everybody is a victim and everybody is a suspect!
summary: A year after the murder of her mother, a teenage girl is terrorized by a new killer, who targets the girl and her friends by using horror films as part of a deadly game.

tagline: Roxanne drives her mother crazy. Maurice never speaks to his niece. Cynthia has a shock for her family. Monica can't talk to her husband. Hortense has never met her mother.
summary: Following the death of her adoptive parents, a successful young black optometrist establishes contact with her biological mother -- a lonely white factory worker living in poverty in East London.

tagline: A true story of the mystery of music and the miracle of love
summary: Pianist David Helfgott, driven by his father and teachers, has a breakdown. Years later he returns to the piano, to popular if not critical acclaim.

tagline: Four friends made a mistake that changed their lives forever.
summary: After a prank goes disastrously wrong, a group of boys are sent to a detention center where they are brutalized. Thirteen years later, an unexpected random encounter with a former guard gives them a chance for revenge.

tagline: A simple man. A difficult choice.
summary: Karl Childers, a simple man hospitalized since his childhood murder of his mother and her lover, is released to start a new life in a small town.

tagline: Together, they just might save the world.
summary: In a desperate attempt to win a basketball match and earn their freedom, the Looney Tunes seek the aid of retired basketball champion, Michael Jordan.

tagline: All the action. All the women. Half the intelligence.
summary: Dick Steele, Agent WD-40 is assigned by his Director, to stop the evil General Rancor from destroying the world. WD-40 believed Rancor was dead and he teams up with the hot K.G.B. Agent Veronique Ukrinsky to find Rancor and save the world.

tagline: There is no thrill like First Contact
summary: The Borg travel back in time intent on preventing Earth's first contact with an alien species. Captain Picard and his crew pursue them to ensure that Zefram Cochrane makes his maiden flight reaching warp speed.

tagline: The most beautiful place to be is in love.
summary: After her mother commits suicide, a young woman travels to Italy in search of love, truth and a deeper connection with herself.

tagline: A stripper raises money needed to get back the one thing she can't live without...her daughter.
summary: A stripper and single mother gets dragged into a dangerous situation after a congressman takes a fancy to her.

tagline: Fight first. Apologize later.
summary: A Chinese chef accidentally gets involved with a news reporter who filmed a drug bust that went awry, and is now being chased by gangs who are trying to get the video tape.

tagline: You're money and you don't even know it!
summary: A wannabe actor has a hard time moving on from a break-up, but he is lucky to have supportive friends.

tagline: Me llamo Ángela. Me van a matar. [English Tagline: My name is Angela.  They're going to kill me.]
summary: While doing a thesis about violence, Ángela finds a snuff video where a girl is tortured until death. Soon she discovers that the girl was a former student in her faculty...

tagline: In every life there comes a time when that dream you dream becomes that thing you do.
summary: A local Pennsylvania band scores a one hit wonder in 1964 and rides the star-making machinery as long as they can, with lots of help from its manager.

tagline: Be careful what you wish for.
summary: An obese attorney is cursed by a gypsy to rapidly and uncontrollably lose weight.

tagline: A lawyer and his assistant fighting to save a father on trial for murder. A time to question what they believe. A time to doubt what they trust. And no time for mistakes.
summary: In Canton, Mississippi, a fearless young lawyer and his assistant defend a black man accused of murdering two white men who raped his ten-year-old daughter, inciting violent retribution and revenge from the Ku Klux Klan.

tagline: Golf pro. Love amateur.
summary: A washed up golf pro working at a driving range tries to qualify for the US Open in order to win the heart of his successful rival's girlfriend.

tagline: Choose life. Choose a job. Choose a starter home. Choose dental insurance, leisure wear and matching luggage. Choose your future. But why would anyone want to do a thing like that?
summary: Renton, deeply immersed in the Edinburgh drug scene, tries to clean up and get out, despite the allure of the drugs and influence of friends.

tagline: Don't Breathe. Don't Look Back.
summary: Bill and Jo Harding, advanced storm chasers on the brink of divorce, must join together to create an advanced weather alert system by putting themselves in the cross-hairs of extremely violent tornadoes.

tagline: There's A Good Reason Some Talent Remains Undiscovered
summary: An aspiring director and the marginally talented amateur cast of a hokey small-town Missouri musical production go overboard when they learn that someone from Broadway will be in attendance.
Follows the personal and professional life of lawyer Ally.

tagline: Get home before dark.
summary: A young woman, destined to slay vampires, demons and other infernal creatures, deals with her life fighting evil, with the help of her friends.
Four friends in a small coastal town help each other cope with adolescence.

tagline: She's got her head in the clouds. He's got his feet on the ground. Together, they're a match made in heaven.
summary: A free-spirited yoga instructor finds true love in a conservative lawyer and they get married on the first date. Though they are polar opposites, he fulfills her need of stability and she fulfills his need of optimism.
The misadventures of a dumb blond egomaniac who is deluded about his own manliness.

tagline: Looking for laughs as big as Texas? Head for the hills!
summary: A straight-laced propane salesman in Arlen, Texas tries to deal with the wacky antics of his family and friends, while also trying to keep his son in line.

tagline: You're inside now.
summary: A series chronicling the daily activities of an unusual prison facility and its criminal inhabitants.

tagline: At the edge of the universe lies a gateway to adventure
summary: A secret military team, SG-1, is formed to explore other planets through the recently discovered Stargates.

tagline: Corrupts Absolutely.
summary: Career thief Luther Whitney (Clint Eastwood) witnesses a horrific crime involving U.S. President Alan Richmond (Gene Hackman).

tagline: The most important man, the surest airplane, the most dangerous Hijackers...
summary: Communist Radicals hijack Air Force One with The U.S. President and his family on board. The Vice President negotiates from Washington D.C., while the President, a Veteran, fights to rescue the hostages on board.

tagline: We are not alone.
summary: 200 years after her death, Ellen Ripley is revived as a powerful human/alien hybrid clone. Along with a crew of space pirates, she must again battle the deadly aliens and stop them from reaching Earth.

tagline: A true story.
summary: In 1839, the revolt of Mende captives aboard a Spanish owned ship causes a major controversy in the United States when the ship is captured off the coast of Long Island. The courts must decide whether the Mende are slaves or legally free.

tagline: It's a SCREAM!
summary: A "National Geographic" film crew is taken hostage by an insane hunter, who forces them along on his quest to capture the world's largest - and deadliest - snake.

tagline: Discover the Adventure Behind the Greatest Mystery of Our Time
summary: The last surviving child of the Russian Royal Family joins two con men to reunite with her grandmother, the Dowager Empress, while the undead Rasputin seeks her death.

tagline: If you don't believe in the existence of evil, you've got a lot to learn.
summary: A boy blackmails his neighbor after suspecting him to be a Nazi war criminal.

primaryTitle: Austin Powers: International Man of Mystery
originalTitle: Austin Powers: International Man of Mystery
tagline: Frozen in the 60's... thawing spring '97, baby!
summary: A world-class playboy and part-time secret agent from the 1960s emerges after thirty years in a cryogenic state to battle with his nemesis Dr. Evil.

tagline: Two amazing secret agents. One diabolical madman. Conditions are dark. The forecast is deadly. Tea, anyone?
summary: Two British Agents team up to stop Sir August de Wynter from destroying the world with a weather-changing machine.

tagline: Think innocent. Think helpless. Think again. Naps are history.
summary: Scientists hold super intelligent talking babies captive, but things take a turn for the worse when a mix-up occurs between a baby genius and its twin.

tagline: Heroes. Villains. Triple Threat.
summary: Batman and Robin try to keep their relationship together even as they must stop Mr. Freeze and Poison Ivy from freezing Gotham City.

tagline: Everything You've Heard Is True
summary: The bumbling Mr. Bean travels to America when he is given the responsibility of bringing a highly valuable painting to a Los Angeles museum.

tagline: Feel the heat, keep the feeling burning, let the sensation explode.
summary: Two neighbors, a woman and a man, form a strong bond after both suspect extramarital activities of their spouses. However, they agree to keep their bond platonic so as not to commit similar wrongs.

tagline: Master of disaster.
summary: A man tries to rescue a woman with a little help from his half brother.

tagline: It takes guys as simple as the Dude and Walter to make a story this complicated... and they'd really rather be bowling.
summary: Jeff "The Dude" Lebowski, mistaken for a millionaire of the same name, seeks restitution for his ruined rug and enlists his bowling buddies to help get it.

tagline: The Blues Are Back
summary: Elwood must reunite the old band, with a few new members, and go on another "Mission from God."

tagline: The life of a dreamer, the days of a business, and the nights in between.
summary: Back when sex was safe, pleasure was a business and business was booming, an idealistic porn producer aspires to elevate his craft to an art when he discovers a hot young talent.

tagline: No-one is safe from chance
summary: A man searches for his missing wife after his car breaks down in the middle of the desert.

tagline: Billy Brown just got out of jail.  Now he's going to serve some real time.  He's going home.
summary: After being released from prison, Billy is set to visit his parents with his wife, whom he does not actually have. This provokes Billy to act out, as he kidnaps a girl and forces her to act as his wife for the visit.

tagline: An unforgettable fable that proves love, family and imagination conquer all.
summary: When an open-minded Jewish librarian and his son become victims of the Holocaust, he uses a perfect mixture of will, humor, and imagination to protect his son from the dangers around their camp.

tagline: Life, love, desire...and everything in between.
summary: After leaving jail, Víctor is still in love with Elena, but she's married to the former cop -now basketball player- who became paralysed by a shot from Víctor's gun...

tagline: Finally, a comedy that tells it like it feels.
summary: Holden and Banky are comic book artists. Everything's going good for them until they meet Alyssa, also a comic book artist. Holden falls for her, but his hopes are crushed when he finds out she's a lesbian.

Matko and his son Zare live on the banks of the Danube river and get by through hustling and basically doing anything to make a living. In order to pay off a business debt Matko agrees to marry off Zare to the sister of a local gangster.

tagline: A Little Secret...Their Biggest Adventure!
summary: After a boy loses his sister's pair of shoes, he goes on a series of adventures in order to find them. When he can't, he tries a new way to "win" a new pair.

tagline: Welcome to Con Air.
summary: Newly paroled ex-con and former U.S. Ranger Cameron Poe finds himself trapped in a prisoner transport plane when the passengers seize control.

tagline: What if your most paranoid nightmares had just come true?
summary: A taxi driver with a penchant for conspiracy theories becomes a target after one of these theories turns out to be true. Unfortunately, to save himself, he has to figure out which theory it is.

tagline: A message from deep space. Who will be the first to go? A journey to the heart of the universe.
summary: Dr. Ellie Arroway, after years of searching, finds conclusive radio proof of extraterrestrial intelligence, sending plans for a mysterious machine.

tagline: No One Is Above The Law.
summary: The Sheriff of a suburban New Jersey community, populated by New York City police officers, slowly discovers the town is a front for mob connections and corruption.

tagline: The pressure is building...
summary: A vulcanologist arrives at a countryside town recently named the second most desirable place to live in America, and discovers that the long dormant volcano, Dante's Peak, may wake up at any moment.

tagline: Darkness Falls Soon
summary: A man struggles with memories of his past, which includes a wife he cannot remember, and a nightmarish world, no one else seems to be waking up from.

tagline: Harry Block wrote a bestseller about his best friends. Now, his best friends are about to become his worst enemies.
summary: Suffering from writer's block and eagerly awaiting his writing award, Harry Block remembers events from his past and scenes from his best-selling books as characters, real and fictional, come back to haunt him.

tagline: Women and children first. You're next.
summary: A group of heavily armed hijackers board a luxury ocean liner in the South Pacific Ocean to loot it, only to do battle with a series of large-sized, tentacled, man-eating sea creatures who had already invaded the ship.

tagline: Devil begins and wins.
summary: An exceptionally adept Florida lawyer is offered a job at a high-end New York City law firm with a high-end boss - the biggest opportunity of his career to date.

tagline: They come from different worlds. They fight for different causes. Now, two men from opposite sides of the law are about to go to war.
summary: A police officer uncovers the real identity of his house-guest, an I.R.A. terrorist in hiding.

tagline: He doesn't just talk to the animals!
summary: A doctor discovers that he can communicate with animals.

tagline: Donnie Brasco. Based On A True Story.
summary: An FBI undercover agent infiltrates the mob and finds himself identifying more with the mafia life, at the expense of his regular one.

tagline: He's a one-man arsenal... with enough voltage to rock the free world.
summary: An international spy teams up with an arms dealer to escape from a penal colony and rescue his family from a terrorist.

tagline: A feast for the senseless.
summary: A few friends have a weekly fools' dinner, where each brings a fool along. Pierre finds a champion fool for next dinner. Surprise.

tagline: They Were Fighting Over A Woman When The Plane Went Down. Now, Their Only Chance For Survival Is Each Other.
summary: An intellectual billionaire and two other men struggle to band together and survive after getting stranded in the Alaskan wilderness with a blood-thirsty Kodiak Bear hunting them down.

tagline: A haunted ship. A missing crew. An infinite evil.
summary: A rescue crew investigates a spaceship that disappeared into a black hole and has now returned...with someone or something new on-board.

tagline: To destroy your enemy, you must find him, face him, and then... become him.
summary: In order to foil a terrorist plot, an FBI agent undergoes facial transplant surgery and assumes the identity of a criminal mastermind, who murdered his only son. The plan turns sour when the criminal wakes up prematurely and seeks revenge.

tagline: Don't trust a soul.
summary: Homicide detective John Hobbes witnesses the execution of serial killer Edgar Reese. Soon after the execution, the killings start again, and they are very similar to Reese's style.

tagline: There is no future without it.
summary: In the colorful future, a cab driver unwittingly becomes the central figure in the search for a legendary cosmic weapon to keep Evil and Mr. Zorg at bay.

tagline: The stuff dreams are made of.
